column2: SELECT TOP # MAX (chinook.Artist.Name) as ArtistName, chinook.Track.AlbumId, count (*) as NUM_TRACKS, SUM (chinook.Track.UnitPrice) TotalPrice FROM chinook.Track INNER JOIN chinook.Album ON chinook.Track.AlbumId = chinook.Album.AlbumId INNER JOIN chinook.Artist ON chinook.Album.ArtistId = chinook.Artist.ArtistId GROUP BY chinook.Track.AlbumId ORDER BY TotalPrice DESC
